<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 15:15:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>官方媒体报道，中国西南购物中心火灾造成至少六人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/least-six-killed-southwest-china-shopping-centre-fire-state-media-reports-2024-07-17/</link><description>中国官方媒体周三报道称，中国西南部的一场购物中心火灾造成至少六人死亡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 14:50:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/least-six-killed-southwest-china-shopping-centre-fire-state-media-reports-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>七国集团贸易部长就解决不公平贸易问题加强对话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-trade-ministers-toughen-talk-tackling-unfair-trade-2024-07-17/</link><description>七国集团（G7）主要民主国家的贸易部长周三表示，如果需要的话，他们将使用“贸易工具”来对抗扭曲市场的做法，与之前的公报相比，措辞更加强硬。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 13:58:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-trade-ministers-toughen-talk-tackling-unfair-trade-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>据《Information》报道，谷歌、微软向中国公司提供 Nvidia 芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/google-microsoft-offer-nvidia-chips-chinese-companies-information-reports-2024-07-17/</link><description>据《The Information》周三报道，谷歌和微软的云部门正在通过在中国境外提供数据中心服务的方式，为中国公司提供使用英伟达人工智能芯片的机会。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 13:36:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/google-microsoft-offer-nvidia-chips-chinese-companies-information-reports-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普对台湾的评论因担心中国收紧限制而下跌 芯片股暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/chip-stocks-tumble-fears-tighter-us-curbs-sales-china-2024-07-17/</link><description>共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普对捍卫台湾态度冷淡，且有报道称华盛顿正在考虑更严格地限制向中国出口先进半导体技术，导致美国芯片股周三下跌逾 4%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 12:20:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/chip-stocks-tumble-fears-tighter-us-curbs-sales-china-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>活动人士呼吁英国政府阻止 Shein 在伦敦上市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/campaigners-call-uk-government-block-sheins-london-listing-2024-07-17/</link><description>由英国零售顾问和电视名人玛丽波塔斯支持的一项新活动发起了一份在线请愿书，呼吁新工党政府阻止快时尚零售商 Shein 在伦敦上市。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 12:14:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/campaigners-call-uk-government-block-sheins-london-listing-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>世贸组织称中国的产业支持计划缺乏透明度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-industrial-support-programmes-lack-transparency-wto-says-2024-07-17/</link><description>世界贸易组织周三表示，由于“总体缺乏透明度”，它无法清楚了解中国对电动汽车或铝和钢铁生产等关键工业部门的财政支持。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 12:06:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-industrial-support-programmes-lack-transparency-wto-says-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>共和党资深议员要求拜登提供在北京僵局中支持菲律宾的选择</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/senior-republican-lawmakers-ask-biden-options-support-philippines-beijing-2024-07-17/</link><description>美国两名高级共和党参议员要求乔·拜登总统提供五角大楼和国务院制定的完整选项清单，以帮助支持菲律宾最近与北京因南海争议浅滩发生的对峙。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 12:04:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/senior-republican-lawmakers-ask-biden-options-support-philippines-beijing-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>戴姆勒卡车股价在指导警告后下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/daimler-truck-shares-fall-after-guidance-warning-2024-07-17/</link><description>德国戴姆勒卡车公司公布其在欧洲销售的卡车的利润率低于预期，并表示其今年的指引目前正在“审查中”，该公司股价周三下跌 4.2%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 12:01:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/daimler-truck-shares-fall-after-guidance-warning-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>大型科技股纳斯达克触及两周低点，芯片股暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/wall-st-futures-slump-after-rally-tech-stocks-slide-2024-07-17/</link><description>周三，纳斯达克指数下跌近 2%，至两周低点，标准普尔 500 指数也随之下跌，原因是美国对让中国获得先进半导体技术的公司实施更严格的贸易限制，这给主要芯片和科技股带来压力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:17:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/wall-st-futures-slump-after-rally-tech-stocks-slide-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>许多美国太阳能工厂都处于落后状态。除了中国拥有的</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/many-us-solar-factories-are-lagging-except-those-china-owns-2024-07-17/</link><description>中国公司在美国兴建的太阳能制造厂数量激增，使中国在这一新兴行业占据主导地位，而其他美国工厂尽管有联邦补贴，仍难以参与竞争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:11:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/many-us-solar-factories-are-lagging-except-those-china-owns-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国在美国拥有的太阳能工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinese-owned-solar-factories-united-states-2024-07-17/</link><description>得益于乔·拜登总统的 2022 年通胀削减法案中包含的新的清洁能源制造补贴，一些最大的中国太阳能电池板制造商正在美国开设工厂。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:09:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinese-owned-solar-factories-united-states-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国太阳能电池板制造商寻求更严格的“美国制造”规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/us-solar-panel-makers-seek-tougher-made-usa-rules-2024-07-17/</link><description>一群美国太阳能制造商呼吁拜登政府加强对使用国产组件的太阳能项目开发商的税收抵免规定，称他们无需使用美国太阳能电池板即可获得税收抵免。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:07:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/us-solar-panel-makers-seek-tougher-made-usa-rules-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：小盘股追赶轮换飙升，特朗普震慑台湾</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-17/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:05:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>美俄新一轮导弹竞赛有多危险？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/arms-race-gathers-pace-russia-us-plan-redeploy-once-banned-weapons-2024-07-17/</link><description>四十年前，美国在欧洲部署了巡航导弹和潘兴 II 核导弹，以对抗苏联的 SS-20 导弹——这一举动加剧了冷战紧张局势，但在几年内就达成了一项历史性的裁军协议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 09:27:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/arms-race-gathers-pace-russia-us-plan-redeploy-once-banned-weapons-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，印度希望为中国技术人员免签</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-looks-free-up-visas-chinese-technicians-sources-say-2024-07-17/</link><description>三名政府官员表示，印度可能会加快对中国技术人员的签证处理，因为印度希望克服制造部门的延误，这些延误阻碍了价值数十亿美元的投资。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 08:32:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-looks-free-up-visas-chinese-technicians-sources-say-2024-07-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>